&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; puli ( english : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; tiger ) is a 2015 indian tamil action &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; thriller film written and directed by suseenthiran starring vishal and kajal aggarwal in the lead roles and samuthirakani , soori and aishwarya dutta in supporting roles . the film was produced by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; movies and distributed by escape artists motion pictures . set in the backdrop of madurai , &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; puli features vishal as an undercover police officer named &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . music for the film was composed by d. imman . the cinematography was led by velraj and the editing by anthony . principal photography commenced on 4 march 2015 and lasted for four months . &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; puli was shot predominantly in and around chennai and other parts of tamil nadu in 75 working days . the film , along with its telugu dubbed version titled jayasurya , was released on 4 september 2015 worldwide . the film has also been dubbed into hindi as main hoon rakshak .